{{Infobox Airport | name = Ouésso Airport | nativename = | image = | IATA = OUE | ICAO = FCOU | type = Public | owner = | operator = Government | city-served = | location = [[Ouésso]] | elevation-f = 1158 | coordinates = {{coord|1|36|55|N|16|02|15|E|type:airport_region:CG|display=inline,title}} | pushpin_map = Republic of the Congo | pushpin_label = '''OUE''' | pushpin_map_caption = Location in the Republic of the Congo | website = | metric-rwy = y | r1-number = 02/20 | r1-length-m = 3000 | r1-surface = Asphalt | footnotes = Source: WAD<ref name="WAD">[http://www.worldaerodata.com/wad.cgi?airport=FCOU Airport information for Ouésso Airport]</ref> GCM<ref name="GCM">{{GCM|OUE|Ouésso Airport}}</ref> Google Maps<ref>[https://www.google.com/maps/@1.6153287,16.0377131,3375m/data=!3m1!1e3 Google Maps - Ouésso]</ref> }}
'''Ouésso Airport''' {{airport codes|OUE|FCOU}} is an airport serving [[Ouésso]], the [[capital city|capital]] of the [[Sangha Department (Congo)|Sangha Department]] in the [[Republic of the Congo]]. Ouésso is on the [[Sangha River]], at the point where it meets the [[Cameroon]] border.
The Cameroon border is less than {{convert|3|km|0}} off the north end of the runway.
The Ouesso [[non-directional beacon]] (Ident: '''OU''') is in the town, {{convert|1.3|nmi|km|1}} east of the airport.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://ourairports.com/navaids/OU/Ouesso_NDB_CG/|title=Ouesso NDB (OU) @ OurAirports|website=ourairports.com|access-date=2018-08-20}}</ref>
