{{Infobox military unit | unit_name = 2nd Motorized Infantry Brigade "Stefan Cel Mare" | image = File:08-27-2016 - Парад в Молдовы 04.jpg | caption = The brigade during the 2016 [[Chișinău Independence Day Parade]]. | dates = 16 October 1992-present | country = {{flag|Moldova}} | branch = [[File:Moldovan Army Flag.gif|23px]] [[Moldovan Ground Forces]] | type = Motorized Infantry | role = | march = | nickname = ''The Stefan Cel Mare Brigade'' | garrison = [[Chisinau]] | commander1 = | identification_symbol = [[File:Moldova09..jpg|border|160px]] | identification_symbol_label = Shoulder Patch | native_name = Brigada 2 Infanterie Motorizată „Stefan Cel Mare” | battles = [[Transnistria War]] | battle_honours = [[File:Ordinul „Credință Patriei”.jpg|23px]] State Order "Faith of the Homeland" 1st class (2017)<ref>http://oficial.md/social/igor-dodon-la-ceremonia-brigazii-2-infanterie-motorizata-stefan-cel-mare-foto</ref> }} The '''2nd Motorized Infantry Brigade "Stefan Cel Mare"''' is an motorized infantry unit of the [[Moldovan National Army]]'s [[Moldovan Ground Forces|Ground Forces]] based in the Moldovan capital of [[Chisinau]]. It was created on October 16, 1992 on the basis of former Soviet units of the Kishinev Garrison.<ref>http://www.army.md/?lng=3&action=show&cat=122&obj=4579#.W66gxctOkex</ref><ref>https://books.google.com/books?id=hm0hAQAAIAAJ&q=Stefan+cel+Mare”+Brigade&dq=Stefan+cel+Mare”+Brigade&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjnv8XQkd_dAhUJ74MKHcgmCI8Q6AEIJzAC</ref> Prior to its official creation, it underwent a 2 month training period, in which the units that now make up the brigade prepared for frontline service in the [[Transnistria War]].
Like all the other motorized infantry brigades in the ground forces, the brigade maintains a military band which serves on special occasions.
